{
  "stem": "268.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Until a few minutes later, or maybe half hour, hour later, I could see my folks packing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They said, we better get out of here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was about 8, 9 o'clock when we first went to the bakery to pick up some goods.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were already closing shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "No one would-- people were panicking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I remember the neighbors who were so friendly, all of a sudden, I remember one neighbor putting on an arm band with a swastika on it and accosting my father with a heil Hitler sign and speaking German all of a sudden.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He forgot Polish overnight.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I can't quite recall what it was.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "But it wasn't complementary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was something like, our time has come now, and all that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So this was a rude awakening.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "We started to pack.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my folks said, we're going-- we have to get out of here, until things calm down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They had no idea what's going to go-- was it going to be a bombing, or will the Hitlerjugend or the Nazi party, which was until then outlawed, it was underground.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "All of a sudden, they came out of the woodwork.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And so we better get out of here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We go back to Czeladz, which was a neighboring town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "As I said, it was like three to four kilometers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And we went on foot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "In fact, this is before automobile.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We didn't have a car, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "If we had, maybe we could have flee to some other country, if there was such a thing, if they let you in.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "But it is dreaming.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we went to this-- took us perhaps something like a hour and a half, two hours-- we were on foot-- to reach that neighboring town, to Czeladz.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
